Package: geobounds
Title: Download Administrative Boundary Data from 'geoBoundaries'
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Diego", "Hernangómez", , "diego.hernangomezherrero@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8457-4658")),
    person("William and Mary geoLab", role = "cph",
           comment = c(ROR = "03hsf0573"))
  )
Description: Tools for downloading individual country files and global
    composite files from 'geoBoundaries' <https://www.geoboundaries.org/>
    across multiple administrative levels. Boundary data are returned as
    'sf' objects for mapping and spatial analysis. See Runfola, D. et al.
    (2020) "geoBoundaries: A global database of political administrative
    boundaries." PLOS ONE 15(4), e0231866.
    <doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0231866>.
